Subject: [PATCH 4.19 27/71] m68knommu: fix overwriting of bits in ColdFire V3 cache control
Date:   Mon, 24 Aug 2020 10:31:18 +0200
Message-Id: <20200824082357.245999635@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.28.0
In-Reply-To: <20200824082355.848475917@linuxfoundation.org>
